{"tid":1255131,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"花澤香菜、竹達彩奈、內田真禮…於2019年迎來30歲的女性聲優一覽","createTime":"2019-06-24T11:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T04:09:46.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d873dacf480ec3fc15070f59e93e87a3a06c2735","tid":1255131,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/76618?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F76618%3F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=bbe9486c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/76618?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/00-29.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F00-29.jpg%3F&h=ee94a949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins>花澤香菜、竹達彩奈、內田真禮&hellip;於2019年迎來30歲的女性聲優一覽</ins></strong><br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 06/01/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B2%E5%84%AA.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2584%25AA.jpg%3F&h=da56a448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當女性由20世代踏入30世代，不免得就會開始考慮結婚生子的事情(如果還未成家立室的話)<br />\n<br />\n有日媒早前就發表了以&rdquo;在2019年迎來30歲的女聲優&rdquo;為題的文章，列出包括花澤香菜、竹達彩奈、內田真禮等十多位將在今年由20世代踏入30世代的女聲優<br />\n<br />\n而在文章內也提到竹達彩奈在2017年被問及有關&rdquo;戀愛禁止&rdquo;的問題時，竹達彩奈回應表示：「事務所的意思感覺是&rdquo;直到30歲前在事業努力&rdquo;」，所以說不定竹達彩奈即將&rdquo;戀愛解禁&rdquo;？<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，花澤香菜在2017年2月22日就已經正式對外公開與男聲優小野賢章交往的消息了<br />\n<strong><ins>超絕朗報，聲優小野賢章與花澤香菜互相正式公開宣佈與對方認真交往中，恭喜恭喜！</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/35789/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F35789%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=662877b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/35789/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>在2019年踏入30世代的女聲優</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n三上枝織(出生：1989年1月6日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%9D%E7%B9%94.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259E%259D%25E7%25B9%2594.jpg%3F&h=26529065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楠田亞衣奈(出生：1989年2月1日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/%E6%A5%A0%E7%94%B0%E4%BA%9E%E8%A1%A3%E5%A5%88.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%25E6%25A5%25A0%25E7%2594%25B0%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%25A5%2588.jpg%3F&h=cad80cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花澤香菜(出生：1989年2月25日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/%E8%8A%B1%E6%BE%A4%E9%A6%99%E8%8F%9C-2.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F%25E8%258A%25B1%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E8%258F%259C-2.jpg%3F&h=eed1e022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n久保百合花(出生：1989年5月19日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/%E4%B9%85%E4%BF%9D%E7%99%BE%E5%90%88%E8%8A%B1.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F%25E4%25B9%2585%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%258A%25B1.jpg%3F&h=030eb450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n石川由依(出生：1989年5月30日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/%E7%9F%B3%E5%B7%9D%E7%94%B1%E4%BE%9D.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%25E7%259F%25B3%25E5%25B7%259D%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25BE%259D.jpg%3F&h=dc0798f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘惠美(出生：1989年6月3日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/%E6%BD%98%E6%83%A0%E7%BE%8E.jpg?\" data-th